<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُتَحَيِّزًا إِلَى فِئَةٍ}</span> ... مُنْحَازًا إِلَى جَمَاعَةِ المُسْلِمِينَ؛ سَوَاءٌ كَانُوا سَرِيَّةً فَانْحَازُوا لِلجَيْشِ أَوِ انْحَازُوا لِلإِمَامِ الأَعْظَمِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَاءَ}</span> ... رَجَعَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَصِيرُ}</span> ... الْمَرْجِعُ، وَالْمَآلُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلِيُبْلِيَ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ}</span> ... لِيُنْعِمَ عَلَيْهِمْ بِالنَّصْرِ وَالأَجْرِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُوهِنُ}</span> ... مُضْعِفُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَسْتَفْتِحُوا}</span> ... تَطْلُبُوا - أَيُّهَا الْكُفَّارُ - مِنَ اللهِ أَنْ يُوقِعَ بَاسَهُ بِالظَّالِمِينَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِئَتُكُمْ}</span> ... جَمَاعَتُكُمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الصُّمُّ}</span> ... الَّذِينَ سُدَّتْ آذَانُهُمْ عَنْ سَمَاعِ الْحَقِّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْبُكْمُ}</span> ... الَّذِينَ خَرِسَتْ أَلْسِنَتُهُمْ عَنِ النُّطْقِ بِالْحَقِّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِتْنَةً}</span> ... مِحْنَةً.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَتَخَطَّفَكُمُ}</span> ... يَاخُذَكُمُ الْكُفَّارُ بِسُرْعَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
